    "## Server Infrastructure\n",
    "\n",
    "## Modify Text (Announcements)\n",
    "\n",
    "The post-login landing text is now **admin-editable in the app UI** (no code edit needed for content changes):\n",
    "\n",
    "1. Log in as admin.\n",
    "2. Open `Administer Projects` -> `Manage Landing Text`.\n",
    "3. Select the panel:\n",
    "   - `Announcement`\n",
    "   - `service_info` (service/instructions panel)\n",
    "4. Add/Edit/Delete/Reorder white text boxes.\n",
    "5. Changes are published immediately and stored in SQLite.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Markdown-lite syntax\n",
    "\n",
    "Use these formats in each box:\n",
    "\n",
    "- Bold: `**important text**`\n",
    "- Bullet list:\n",
    "  - `- first item`\n",
    "  - `- second item`\n",
    "- Numbered list:\n",
    "  - `1. first`\n",
    "  - `2. second`\n",
    "- Link: `[@NGS](mailto:ngs@example.org)`\n",
    "\n",
    "### Where it is stored\n",
    "\n",
    "- DB tables:\n",
    "  - `announcement_panels`\n",
    "  - `announcement_items`\n",
    "- App render + admin handlers:\n",
    "  - `/Users/exampleuser/Documents/Github/example-repo/sequencing-app/app.R`\n",
    "- Style classes (unchanged):\n",
    "  - `.announcement-panel`\n",
    "  - `.service-panel`\n",
    "  - `.info-box`\n",
    "\n",
    "If tables are missing, the app auto-creates them and seeds default content on startup.\n",
    "\n",
    "### SQL handling (moved)\n",
    "\n",
    "All SQL database commands and explanations were moved to **`notes/sql-handling.qmd`**.  \n",
    "This includes:\n",
    "\n",
    "- DB rebuild procedure\n",
    "- Admin user promotion in LDAP mode\n",
    "- Budget holder updates (CSV vs DB)\n",
    "- SQLite inspection and maintenance commands\n",
    "### Install required system dependencies\n",
    "\n",
